## SECTION 2 — SCOPE

This License governs all Materials associated with or produced under the
following systems, frameworks, and identities:

| Element | Definition |
|---|---|
| **LUWO Framework** | Named unified system of layered waveforms and oscillations, including all methodology, documentation, and architectural specifications |
| **LUWO Golden Curve (JGC)** | Unified geometric expression combining phi-stretched parabolas, fractal golden spirals, non-Euclidean curves, and biological propagation patterns, including all parametric and closed-form representations |
| **Wolf Pi (π_l = 3.14466)** | Distinct irrational constant, its derivations, geometric extensions, and all computational implementations thereof |
| **Dragon Engine** | Execution, research loop, and automation architecture and all associated subsystems |
| **Wolf Engine** | Oversight, optimization, and tuning architecture and all associated subsystems |
| **Ronin Engine** | Dual-action logic, movement core, and advanced operations architecture and all associated subsystems |
| **LUWO Sigil System** | Visual language, glyph framework, rendering methodology, and all associated symbolic representations |
| **Primordial Protocol** | Multi-bot crypto intelligence ecosystem built on the LUWO engine, including all bot tiers (Wolf Take, Ronin, Veyra, and all Cybergenetic classifications) |

